<item>
            <title>[HADOOP-10031] FsShell -get/copyToLocal/moveFromLocal should support Windows local path</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-10031</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In current trunk code, running &apos;hadoop fs -get /hdfs/path c:\windows\path&apos; will lead to an error put: unexpected URISyntaxException. This is a regression to the 1.0 fs shell commands. FsShell get, copyToLocal, and moveFromLocal should support Windows local path formats as localSrc argument to the two commands.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
